<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>永旺</title><link>https://aeon.co/feed.atom</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 18:13:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>为什么亨利八世的密码如此具有纪念意义</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/why-a-forcefully-phallic-portrait-of-henry-viii-is-a-masterful-work-of-propaganda?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/c9814b30-d53c-4025-bb65-755f59712bb2/header_why-henry-viii_s-codpiece-is-so-monumental-lansdcape-1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;亨利八世的强大密码宣告了他的性、政治和精神力量，而当时这三者都受到质疑&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/why-a-forcefully-phallic-portrait-of-henry-viii-is-a-masterful-work-of-propaganda?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/why-a-forcefully-phallic-portrait-of-henry-viii-is-a-masterful-work-of-propaganda?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>脱离</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/why-we-must-seize-leisurely-interludes-from-works-confines?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="沙滩上，一名身穿牛仔裤、赤裸上身的男子睡在他 1970 年代的汽车旁边" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/889b290f-bb8f-4b2d-9f2e-2f07e1798872/header_essay-v2-nyc13780.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;现代生活让我们面临着一切消耗性的需求。这就是为什么我们应该反思远离这一切意味着什么&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——大卫·J·西格尔&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/why-we-must-seize-leisurely-interludes-from-works-confines?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/why-we-must-seize-leisurely-interludes-from-works-confines?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>神秘的园艺艺术</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/a-rebel-spirit-and-an-artists-eye-russell-pages-landscape-design?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="两座狮身人面像般的雕像前景是一个复杂的正式花园，花园里有几何树篱和一个方形池塘。背景是盛开的樱花树" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/0eb69a89-5f85-4594-a982-04a8c93d4ceb/header_essay-v1-blossom.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;在 20 世纪郊区扩张的时代，伟大的设计师拉塞尔·佩奇 (Russell Page) 将深情的哲学注入他的花园&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——凯莱布·史密斯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/a-rebel-spirit-and-an-artists-eye-russell-pages-landscape-design?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/a-rebel-spirit-and-an-artists-eye-russell-pages-landscape-design?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>细胞世界</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/explore-a-bioluminescent-world-of-cellular-life-via-cutting-edge-microscopy?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/b1212f79-d7c0-43b7-af91-970638d6d2af/header_cell-worlds-landscape-3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;科学技术与艺术的融合，带来一场令人眼花缭乱的“隐藏在我们每个人心中”的微观星系之旅&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/explore-a-bioluminescent-world-of-cellular-life-via-cutting-edge-microscopy?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/explore-a-bioluminescent-world-of-cellular-life-via-cutting-edge-microscopy?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>你是艺术天才吗？</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/you-can-be-truly-creative-if-you-let-go-of-your-assumptions?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/d6b37363-a465-4579-8cc5-cf1ba3e16207/header_essay-gettyimages-1315366028.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;也许不是，但如果这是你在生活中发挥创造力的门槛，那么你就完全错了&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——詹姆斯·C·考夫曼&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/you-can-be-truly-creative-if-you-let-go-of-your-assumptions?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/you-can-be-truly-creative-if-you-let-go-of-your-assumptions?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>保罗·菲佛：中断广播</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/a-unique-project-frames-college-football-as-an-intricately-choreographed-mass-ritual?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/3ee60bba-1e91-4b2e-85aa-a1d2375a253f/header_paul-pfeiffer-interrupting-the-broadcast-landscape-4.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;现场体育赛事的巧妙制作如何操纵观众的情绪，创造近乎宗教的体验&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/a-unique-project-frames-college-football-as-an-intricately-choreographed-mass-ritual?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/a-unique-project-frames-college-football-as-an-intricately-choreographed-mass-ritual?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>最后的道德边界</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/as-space-gets-more-commercial-how-can-it-be-governed-ethically?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="玻璃穹顶下的人物观看火箭从火星表面发射" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/cb72851c-2cd7-4df9-bdc1-11b30a81fbc7/header_essay-spacex-on-mars-qalnmz8hsnj8zuggdpiftj.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;地球探索受到殖民主义、剥削和榨取的困扰。我们能希望让空间变得不同吗？&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;——菲利普·鲍尔&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/as-space-gets-more-commercial-how-can-it-be-governed-ethically?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/as-space-gets-more-commercial-how-can-it-be-governed-ethically?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>欧文·芬克尔的古代恶魔</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/meet-the-absentee-gods-and-nefarious-spirits-of-ancient-mesopotamia?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/916e16b0-51bd-473b-9900-c3e47be6d91a/header_ancient-demons-with-irving-finkel-landscape-3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;有趣的亚述学家欧文·芬克尔解开了古代美索不达米亚缺席的诸神和爱管闲事的灵魂的网络&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/meet-the-absentee-gods-and-nefarious-spirits-of-ancient-mesopotamia?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/meet-the-absentee-gods-and-nefarious-spirits-of-ancient-mesopotamia?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>已经看过</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/deja-vu-a-window-on-the-past-and-a-key-to-human-survival?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="床上放着一顶巴拿马帽，午后的阳光透过纱帘照射进来。有轻微的运动模糊" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/bed33711-15d1-4efb-9558-a206aab8b454/header_test-nn11556269.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;你有没有来过这里？那种怪异的感觉是你的心灵在向内寻找自己生存的线索的影子&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——安妮·克利里&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/deja-vu-a-window-on-the-past-and-a-key-to-human-survival?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/deja-vu-a-window-on-the-past-and-a-key-to-human-survival?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>与相对主义的斗争</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/bernard-williams-moral-relativism-and-the-culture-wars?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/86d431d8-d3cd-4891-8f6b-aabd112c5c66/header_essay-goya-6985.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;伯纳德·威廉姆斯认为，一个人的道德是由文化和历史塑造的。但这并不意味着每个人都是对的&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——丹尼尔·卡尔卡特&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/bernard-williams-moral-relativism-and-the-culture-wars?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/bernard-williams-moral-relativism-and-the-culture-wars?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item></channel></rss>